Package: fmap
Title: Fresnel Maps with Equal-Area Concentric Circles
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Liam", "Bolton", , "liamthomasbolton@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: fmap is a package for producing Fresnel Maps, a new thematic mapping technique in which data is visualised to the level of equal-area concentric circles or doughnuts.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    sf,
    tmap
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
